abstract: Reports will include existing home sales for September and corporate results from Ford, Procter & Gamble, Microsoft and Exxon Mobil.
snippet: Reports will include existing home sales for September and corporate results from Ford, Procter & Gamble, Microsoft and Exxon Mobil.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC REPORTS Data will include existing home sales for September from the National Association of Realtors (Monday); the Standard & Poor’s/Case-Shiller index of home prices for August and the Consumer Confidence Index (Tuesday); durable goods for September and new home sales for September from the government (Wednesday); weekly jobless claims (Thursday); and third-quarter gross domestic product (Friday).

headline.main: Looking Ahead: Economic Reports This Week
